      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2021 Honda Accord in poor condition. The exterior has noticeable dents, scratches, and body damage in multiple areas. The interior shows significant wear including damaged upholstery, staining, and worn surfaces. Mechanical components have issues that will require attention. Suitable for buyers willing to invest in repairs.",
