    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in good condition. It runs reliably and drives well. The exterior has a few light surface scratches and minor cosmetic blemishes, but no significant dents or rust. The interior shows some normal wear on the seats and surfaces, but remains clean and functional. All major mechanical systems are operating properly.",
